sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Database

    Client->>API: PATCH /carts/{cartId}/items/{itemId} (UpdateItemRequest)
    API->>Database: UPDATE cart_items SET quantity = $1, updated_at = NOW() WHERE id = $2 AND cart_id = $3 RETURNING *
    Database-->>API: updated cart_items row (or not found)
    alt item not found
        API-->>Client: 404 Not Found (ProblemDetail)
    else item updated
        API-->>Client: 200 OK (CartItem)
    end
